{
  "video_id": "urntcMUJR9M",
  "title": "5 ways to lead in an era of constant change | Jim Hemerling",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12825.0,
      "end_time": 15200.0,
      "text": "Have you ever noticed when you ask someone to talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15200.0,
      "end_time": 18560.0,
      "text": "about a change they&#39;re making for the better in their personal lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18560.0,
      "end_time": 21015.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re often really energetic?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21015.0,
      "end_time": 23520.0,
      "text": "Whether it&#39;s training for a marathon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23520.0,
      "end_time": 24800.0,
      "text": "picking up an old hobby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24800.0,
      "end_time": 26680.0,
      "text": "or learning a new skill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26680.0,
      "end_time": 27960.0,
      "text": "for most people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27960.0,
      "end_time": 33720.0,
      "text": "self-transformation projects occupy a very positive emotional space."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33720.0,
      "end_time": 36200.0,
      "text": "Self-transformation is empowering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36200.0,
      "end_time": 38560.0,
      "text": "energizing, even exhilarating."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38560.0,
      "end_time": 42360.0,
      "text": "I mean just take a look at some of the titles of self-help books:"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42360.0,
      "end_time": 45080.0,
      "text": "&quot;Awaken the Giant Within,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45080.0,
      "end_time": 47600.0,
      "text": "&quot;Practicing the Power of Now,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47600.0,
      "end_time": 50080.0,
      "text": "or here&#39;s a great one we can all relate to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50080.0,
      "end_time": 52320.0,
      "text": "&quot;You are a Badass:"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52320.0,
      "end_time": 57440.0,
      "text": "How to Stop Doubting Your Greatness and Start Living an Awesome Life.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57440.0,
      "end_time": 60040.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60040.0,
      "end_time": 63240.0,
      "text": "When it comes to self-transformation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63240.0,
      "end_time": 68840.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t help but get a sense of the excitement."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68840.0,
      "end_time": 72040.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s another type of transformation"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72040.0,
      "end_time": 76080.0,
      "text": "that occupies a very different emotional space."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76080.0,
      "end_time": 79880.0,
      "text": "The transformation of organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79880.0,
      "end_time": 81240.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re like most people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81240.0,
      "end_time": 85640.0,
      "text": "when you hear the words &quot;Our organization is going to start a transformation,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85640.0,
      "end_time": 87426.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re thinking, &quot;Uh-oh.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87426.0,
      "end_time": 88600.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88600.0,
      "end_time": 90800.0,
      "text": "&quot;Layoffs.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90800.0,
      "end_time": 92760.0,
      "text": "The blood drains from your face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 92760.0,
      "end_time": 95640.0,
      "text": "your mind goes into overdrive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95640.0,
      "end_time": 100120.0,
      "text": "frantically searching for some place to run and hide."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 100120.0,
      "end_time": 101640.0,
      "text": "Well, you can run,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101640.0,
      "end_time": 104040.0,
      "text": "but you really can&#39;t hide."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104040.0,
      "end_time": 107040.0,
      "text": "Most of us spend the majority of our waking hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 107040.0,
      "end_time": 109040.0,
      "text": "involved in organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109040.0,
      "end_time": 112160.0,
      "text": "And due to changes in globalization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112160.0,
      "end_time": 114720.0,
      "text": "changes due to advances in technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114720.0,
      "end_time": 116560.0,
      "text": "and other factors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116560.0,
      "end_time": 122360.0,
      "text": "the reality is our organizations are constantly having to adapt."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122360.0,
      "end_time": 123600.0,
      "text": "In fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 123600.0,
      "end_time": 129400.0,
      "text": "I call this the era of &quot;always-on&quot; transformation."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 129400.0,
      "end_time": 131680.0,
      "text": "When I shared this idea with my wife Nicola,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 131680.0,
      "end_time": 134840.0,
      "text": "she said, &quot;Always-on transformation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 134840.0,
      "end_time": 137640.0,
      "text": "That sounds exhausting.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 137640.0,
      "end_time": 139960.0,
      "text": "And that may be exactly what you&#39;re thinking --"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139960.0,
      "end_time": 141560.0,
      "text": "and you would be right."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 141560.0,
      "end_time": 146720.0,
      "text": "Particularly if we continue to approach the transformation of organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 146720.0,
      "end_time": 148920.0,
      "text": "the way we always have been."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148920.0,
      "end_time": 151360.0,
      "text": "But because we can&#39;t hide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 151360.0,
      "end_time": 153080.0,
      "text": "we need to sort out two things."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153080.0,
      "end_time": 154320.0,
      "text": "First,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 154320.0,
      "end_time": 157080.0,
      "text": "why is transformation so exhausting?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 157080.0,
      "end_time": 161200.0,
      "text": "And second, how do we fix it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 161200.0,
      "end_time": 162440.0,
      "text": "First of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 162440.0,
      "end_time": 165600.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s acknowledge that change is hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 165600.0,
      "end_time": 167640.0,
      "text": "People naturally resist change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 167640.0,
      "end_time": 171200.0,
      "text": "especially when it&#39;s imposed on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 171200.0,
      "end_time": 175800.0,
      "text": "But there are things that organizations do that make change even harder"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 175800.0,
      "end_time": 179720.0,
      "text": "and more exhausting for people than it needs to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 179720.0,
      "end_time": 180960.0,
      "text": "First of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 180960.0,
      "end_time": 185040.0,
      "text": "leaders often wait too long to act."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185040.0,
      "end_time": 186280.0,
      "text": "As a result,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 186280.0,
      "end_time": 190320.0,
      "text": "everything is happening in crisis mode."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 190320.0,
      "end_time": 193360.0,
      "text": "Which, of course, tends to be exhausting."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 193360.0,
      "end_time": 196480.0,
      "text": "Or, given the urgency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 196480.0,
      "end_time": 201320.0,
      "text": "what they&#39;ll do is they&#39;ll just focus on the short-term results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 201320.0,
      "end_time": 204560.0,
      "text": "but that doesn&#39;t give any hope for the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 204560.0,
      "end_time": 209040.0,
      "text": "Or they&#39;ll just take a superficial, one-off approach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 209040.0,
      "end_time": 213160.0,
      "text": "hoping that they can return back to business as usual"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 213160.0,
      "end_time": 217600.0,
      "text": "as soon as the crisis is over."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 217600.0,
      "end_time": 218840.0,
      "text": "This kind of approach"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 218840.0,
      "end_time": 226280.0,
      "text": "is kind of the way some students approach preparing for standardized tests."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 226280.0,
      "end_time": 229760.0,
      "text": "In order to get test scores to go up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 229760.0,
      "end_time": 233160.0,
      "text": "teachers will end up teaching to the test."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 233160.0,
      "end_time": 234560.0,
      "text": "Now, that approach can work;"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 234560.0,
      "end_time": 236520.0,
      "text": "test results often do go up."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 236520.0,
      "end_time": 240320.0,
      "text": "But it fails the fundamental goal of education:"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 240320.0,
      "end_time": 246680.0,
      "text": "to prepare students to succeed over the long term."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 246680.0,
      "end_time": 250160.0,
      "text": "So given these obstacles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 250160.0,
      "end_time": 252000.0,
      "text": "what can we do"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 252000.0,
      "end_time": 255480.0,
      "text": "to transform the way we transform organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 255480.0,
      "end_time": 258200.0,
      "text": "so rather than being exhausting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 258200.0,
      "end_time": 262160.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s actually empowering and energizing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 262160.0,
      "end_time": 267200.0,
      "text": "To do that, we need to focus on five strategic imperatives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 267200.0,
      "end_time": 269959.0,
      "text": "all of which have one thing in common:"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 269959.0,
      "end_time": 273079.0,
      "text": "putting people first."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 273079.0,
      "end_time": 275760.0,
      "text": "The first imperative for putting people first"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 275760.0,
      "end_time": 278120.0,
      "text": "is to inspire through purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 278120.0,
      "end_time": 281840.0,
      "text": "Most transformations have financial and operational goals."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 281840.0,
      "end_time": 286120.0,
      "text": "These are important and they can be energizing to leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 286120.0,
      "end_time": 290480.0,
      "text": "but they tend not to be very motivating to most people in the organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 290480.0,
      "end_time": 292280.0,
      "text": "To motivate more broadly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 292280.0,
      "end_time": 297720.0,
      "text": "the transformation needs to connect with a deeper sense of purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 297720.0,
      "end_time": 299640.0,
      "text": "Take LEGO."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 299640.0,
      "end_time": 304520.0,
      "text": "The LEGO Group has become an extraordinary global company."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 304520.0,
      "end_time": 306280.0,
      "text": "Under their very capable leadership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 306280.0,
      "end_time": 309800.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve actually undergone a series of transformations."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 309800.0,
      "end_time": 313040.0,
      "text": "While each of these has had a very specific focus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 313040.0,
      "end_time": 314360.0,
      "text": "the North Star,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 314360.0,
      "end_time": 316200.0,
      "text": "linking and guiding all of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 316200.0,
      "end_time": 319480.0,
      "text": "has been Lego&#39;s powerful purpose:"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 319480.0,
      "end_time": 324360.0,
      "text": "inspire and develop the builders of tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 324360.0,
      "end_time": 326160.0,
      "text": "Expanding globally?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 326160.0,
      "end_time": 328600.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not about increasing sales,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 328600.0,
      "end_time": 333960.0,
      "text": "but about giving millions of additional children access to LEGO building bricks."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 333960.0,
      "end_time": 335960.0,
      "text": "Investment and innovation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 335960.0,
      "end_time": 338360.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not about developing new products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 338360.0,
      "end_time": 340680.0,
      "text": "but about enabling more children"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 340680.0,
      "end_time": 345440.0,
      "text": "to experience the joy of learning through play."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 345440.0,
      "end_time": 347000.0,
      "text": "Not surprisingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 347000.0,
      "end_time": 354120.0,
      "text": "that deep sense of purpose tends to be highly motivating to LEGO&#39;s people."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 354120.0,
      "end_time": 357080.0,
      "text": "The second imperative for putting people first"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 357080.0,
      "end_time": 360080.0,
      "text": "is to go all in."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 360080.0,
      "end_time": 361800.0,
      "text": "Too many transformations"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 361800.0,
      "end_time": 365560.0,
      "text": "are nothing more than head-count cutting exercises;"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 365560.0,
      "end_time": 369960.0,
      "text": "layoffs under the guise of transformation."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 369960.0,
      "end_time": 372040.0,
      "text": "In the face of relentless competition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 372040.0,
      "end_time": 376000.0,
      "text": "it may well be that you will have to take the painful decision"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 376000.0,
      "end_time": 378880.0,
      "text": "to downsize the organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 378880.0,
      "end_time": 384000.0,
      "text": "just as you may have to lose some weight in order to run a marathon."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 384000.0,
      "end_time": 385240.0,
      "text": "But losing weight alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 385240.0,
      "end_time": 388560.0,
      "text": "will not get you across the finish line with a winning time."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 388560.0,
      "end_time": 390160.0,
      "text": "To win"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 390160.0,
      "end_time": 392880.0,
      "text": "you need to go all in."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 392880.0,
      "end_time": 397160.0,
      "text": "You need to go all in."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 397160.0,
      "end_time": 399640.0,
      "text": "Rather than just cutting costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 399640.0,
      "end_time": 402200.0,
      "text": "you need to think about initiatives"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 402200.0,
      "end_time": 404920.0,
      "text": "that will enable you to win in the medium term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 404920.0,
      "end_time": 406920.0,
      "text": "initiatives to drive growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 406920.0,
      "end_time": 411000.0,
      "text": "actions that will fundamentally change the way the company operates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 411000.0,
      "end_time": 412560.0,
      "text": "and very importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 412560.0,
      "end_time": 418680.0,
      "text": "investments to develop the leadership and the talent."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 418680.0,
      "end_time": 422480.0,
      "text": "The third imperative for putting people first"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 422480.0,
      "end_time": 425200.0,
      "text": "is to enable people with the capabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 425200.0,
      "end_time": 432280.0,
      "text": "that they need to succeed during the transformation and beyond."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 432280.0,
      "end_time": 436280.0,
      "text": "Over the years I&#39;ve competed in a number of triathlons."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 436280.0,
      "end_time": 438480.0,
      "text": "You know, frankly, I&#39;m not that good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 438480.0,
      "end_time": 442520.0,
      "text": "but I do have one distinct capability;"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 442520.0,
      "end_time": 446640.0,
      "text": "I am remarkably fast at finding my bike."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 446640.0,
      "end_time": 448560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 448560.0,
      "end_time": 450400.0,
      "text": "By the time I finish the swim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 450400.0,
      "end_time": 452280.0,
      "text": "almost all the bikes are already gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 452280.0,
      "end_time": 456160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 456160.0,
      "end_time": 460240.0,
      "text": "Real triathletes know that each leg --"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 460240.0,
      "end_time": 462000.0,
      "text": "the swim, the bike, the run --"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 462000.0,
      "end_time": 464520.0,
      "text": "really requires different capabilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 464520.0,
      "end_time": 465760.0,
      "text": "different tools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 465760.0,
      "end_time": 468440.0,
      "text": "different skills, different techniques."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 468440.0,
      "end_time": 470920.0,
      "text": "Likewise when we transform organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 470920.0,
      "end_time": 473800.0,
      "text": "we need to be sure that we&#39;re giving our people"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 473800.0,
      "end_time": 478160.0,
      "text": "the skills and the tools they need along the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 478160.0,
      "end_time": 479400.0,
      "text": "Chronos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 479400.0,
      "end_time": 481400.0,
      "text": "a global software company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 481400.0,
      "end_time": 486360.0,
      "text": "recognized the need to transfer from building products --"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 486360.0,
      "end_time": 488040.0,
      "text": "software products --"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 488040.0,
      "end_time": 491800.0,
      "text": "to building software as a service."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 491800.0,
      "end_time": 495040.0,
      "text": "To enable its people to take that transformation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 495040.0,
      "end_time": 497760.0,
      "text": "first of all they invested in new tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 497760.0,
      "end_time": 502840.0,
      "text": "that would enable their employees to monitor the usage of the features"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 502840.0,
      "end_time": 506280.0,
      "text": "as well as customer satisfaction with the new service."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 506280.0,
      "end_time": 510000.0,
      "text": "They also invested in skill development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 510000.0,
      "end_time": 511840.0,
      "text": "so that their employees would be able"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 511840.0,
      "end_time": 514960.0,
      "text": "to resolve customer service problems on the spot."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 514960.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516200.00000000006,
      "text": "And very importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 516200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519600.00000000006,
      "text": "they also reinforced the collaborative behaviors that would be required"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 519600.0,
      "end_time": 524679.0,
      "text": "to deliver an end-to-end seamless customer experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 524679.0,
      "end_time": 526280.0,
      "text": "Because of these investments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 526280.0,
      "end_time": 529640.0,
      "text": "rather than feeling overwhelmed by the transformation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 529640.0,
      "end_time": 532919.0,
      "text": "Chronos employees actually felt energized"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 532919.0,
      "end_time": 536200.0,
      "text": "and empowered in their new roles."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 536200.0,
      "end_time": 538440.0,
      "text": "In the era of &quot;always-on&quot; transformation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 538440.0,
      "end_time": 539960.0,
      "text": "change is a constant."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 539960.0,
      "end_time": 541920.0,
      "text": "My fourth imperative therefore"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 541920.0,
      "end_time": 546800.0,
      "text": "is to instill a culture of continuous learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 546800.0,
      "end_time": 549840.0,
      "text": "When Satya Nadella became the CEO of Microsoft"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 549840.0,
      "end_time": 551800.0,
      "text": "in February 2014,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 551800.0,
      "end_time": 554720.0,
      "text": "he embarked on an ambitious transformation journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 554720.0,
      "end_time": 559640.0,
      "text": "to prepare the company to compete in a mobile-first, cloud-first world."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 559640.0,
      "end_time": 561960.0,
      "text": "This included changes to strategy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 561960.0,
      "end_time": 563200.0,
      "text": "the organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 563200.0,
      "end_time": 566280.0,
      "text": "and very importantly, the culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 566280.0,
      "end_time": 571320.0,
      "text": "Microsoft&#39;s culture at the time was one of silos and internal competition --"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 571320.0,
      "end_time": 574480.0,
      "text": "not exactly conducive to learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 574480.0,
      "end_time": 577560.0,
      "text": "Nadella took this head-on."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 577560.0,
      "end_time": 581000.0,
      "text": "He rallied his leadership around his vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 581000.0,
      "end_time": 584240.0,
      "text": "for a living, learning culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 584240.0,
      "end_time": 586600.0,
      "text": "shifting from a fixed mindset,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 586600.0,
      "end_time": 590000.0,
      "text": "where your role was to show up as the smartest person in the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 590000.0,
      "end_time": 591840.0,
      "text": "to a growth mindset,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 591840.0,
      "end_time": 598720.0,
      "text": "where your role was to listen, to learn and to bring out the best in people."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 598720.0,
      "end_time": 600000.0,
      "text": "Well, early days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 600000.0,
      "end_time": 604080.0,
      "text": "Microsoft employees already noticed this shift in the culture --"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 604080.0,
      "end_time": 608560.0,
      "text": "clear evidence of Microsoft putting people first."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 608560.0,
      "end_time": 613200.0,
      "text": "My fifth and final imperative is specifically for leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 613200.0,
      "end_time": 614880.0,
      "text": "In a transformation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 614880.0,
      "end_time": 617160.0,
      "text": "a leader needs to have a vision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 617160.0,
      "end_time": 620600.0,
      "text": "a clear road map with milestones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 620600.0,
      "end_time": 625080.0,
      "text": "and then you need to hold people accountable for results."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 625080.0,
      "end_time": 628240.0,
      "text": "In other words, you need to be directive."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 628240.0,
      "end_time": 631400.0,
      "text": "But in order to capture the hearts and minds of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 631400.0,
      "end_time": 634680.0,
      "text": "you also need to be inclusive."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 634680.0,
      "end_time": 639920.0,
      "text": "Inclusive leadership is critical to putting people first."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 639920.0,
      "end_time": 642680.0,
      "text": "I live in the San Francisco Bay area."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 642680.0,
      "end_time": 643920.0,
      "text": "And right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 643920.0,
      "end_time": 646960.0,
      "text": "our basketball team is the best in the league."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 646960.0,
      "end_time": 649640.0,
      "text": "We won the 2015 championship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 649640.0,
      "end_time": 652600.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re favored to win again this year."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 652600.0,
      "end_time": 654680.0,
      "text": "There are many explanations for this."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 654680.0,
      "end_time": 657120.0,
      "text": "They have some fabulous players,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 657120.0,
      "end_time": 658920.0,
      "text": "but one of the key reasons"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 658920.0,
      "end_time": 665360.0,
      "text": "is their head coach, Steve Kerr, is an inclusive leader."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 665360.0,
      "end_time": 668000.0,
      "text": "When Kerr came to the Warriors in 2014,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 668000.0,
      "end_time": 671480.0,
      "text": "the Warriors were looking for a major transformation."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 671480.0,
      "end_time": 677640.0,
      "text": "They hadn&#39;t won a national championship since 1975."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 677640.0,
      "end_time": 680840.0,
      "text": "Kerr came in, and he had a clear vision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 680840.0,
      "end_time": 684480.0,
      "text": "and he immediately got to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 684480.0,
      "end_time": 685840.0,
      "text": "From the outset,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 685840.0,
      "end_time": 689960.0,
      "text": "he reached out and engaged the players and the staff."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 689960.0,
      "end_time": 695360.0,
      "text": "He created an environment of open debate and solicited suggestions."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 695360.0,
      "end_time": 697080.0,
      "text": "During games he would often ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 697080.0,
      "end_time": 700000.0,
      "text": "&quot;What are you seeing that I&#39;m missing?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 700000.0,
      "end_time": 706600.0,
      "text": "One the best examples of this came in game four of the 2015 finals."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 706600.0,
      "end_time": 709880.0,
      "text": "The Warriors were down two games to one"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 709880.0,
      "end_time": 714600.0,
      "text": "when Kerr made the decision to change the starting lineup;"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 714600.0,
      "end_time": 719360.0,
      "text": "a bold move by any measure."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 719360.0,
      "end_time": 722960.0,
      "text": "The Warriors won the game and went on to win the championship."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 722960.0,
      "end_time": 724240.0,
      "text": "And it is widely viewed"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 724240.0,
      "end_time": 729440.0,
      "text": "that that move was the pivotal move in their victory."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 729440.0,
      "end_time": 734560.0,
      "text": "Interestingly, it wasn&#39;t actually Kerr&#39;s idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 734560.0,
      "end_time": 739160.0,
      "text": "It was the idea of his 28-year-old assistant, Nick U&#39;Ren."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 739160.0,
      "end_time": 741360.0,
      "text": "Because of Kerr&#39;s leadership style,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 741360.0,
      "end_time": 745240.0,
      "text": "U&#39;Ren felt comfortable bringing the idea forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 745240.0,
      "end_time": 747240.0,
      "text": "And Kerr not only listened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 747240.0,
      "end_time": 749520.0,
      "text": "but he implemented the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 749520.0,
      "end_time": 751200.0,
      "text": "and then afterwards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 751200.0,
      "end_time": 754520.0,
      "text": "gave U&#39;Ren all the credit --"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 754520.0,
      "end_time": 761280.0,
      "text": "actions all consistent with Kerr&#39;s highly inclusive approach to leadership."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 761280.0,
      "end_time": 763960.0,
      "text": "In the era of &quot;always-on&quot; transformation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 763960.0,
      "end_time": 769200.0,
      "text": "organizations are always going to be transforming."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 769200.0,
      "end_time": 774080.0,
      "text": "But doing so does not have to be exhausting."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 774080.0,
      "end_time": 776280.0,
      "text": "We owe it to ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 776280.0,
      "end_time": 778280.0,
      "text": "to our organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 778280.0,
      "end_time": 781000.0,
      "text": "and to society more broadly"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 781000.0,
      "end_time": 785920.0,
      "text": "to boldly transform our approach to transformation."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 785920.0,
      "end_time": 787600.0,
      "text": "To do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 787600.0,
      "end_time": 791800.0,
      "text": "we need to start putting people first."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 791800.0,
      "end_time": 793040.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 793040.0,
      "end_time": 803040.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}